[[File:ChagrianPerformerSpy-CaM.png|thumb|right|250px|A Chagrian stage performer.]]
An '''entertainer''' was a person who performed in front of audiences for money. It was a general term that could be applied to singers, dancers, [[Musician/Legends|musicians]] and [[Acrobat/Legends|acrobats]]. One famous band was [[Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes/Legends|Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes]]. For some species, entertaining was a way of life. One well known species who considered this were the [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]]. Bith were known to play musical instruments, and were known as some of the best musicians in the galaxy (Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes were Bith).

